    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "af64a0ad_e7684069",
        "filename": "milo/git/fetch_refs.go",
        "patchSetId": 13
      },
      "lineNbr": 142,
      "author": {
        "id": 1153089
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-06-22T22:46:50Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "In general case, we\u0027ll have a lot more commits than the limit. Sorting slice that contains all commits will therefore be also sorting many commits that we do not need. Also sorting is O(nk*log(nk)), where n is the limit and k is the number of fetched refs, whereas max-heap merging is O(nk*log(k)).",
      "parentUuid": "d4b13e93_794ec404",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 125,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 142,
        "endChar": 2
      },
      "revId": "3f84e25dc12859a1c277a5a0125a462ed11c4e67",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
      "unresolved": true
